parameters.name: Year
parameters.description: Spacecraft event year given in PDS time format (yy).

parameters.name: Day
parameters.description: Spacecraft day of year starting from 1972 (ddd).

parameters.name: Hour
parameters.description: Spacecraft hour of day in format (hh).

parameters.name: Minute
parameters.description: Spacecraft minute of hour in format (mm).

parameters.name: SC
parameters.description: Spacecraft second of minute in format (ss).

parameters.name: Delay
parameters.description:
One-way time delay at daily intervals for radio signal to travel 
                    between the Earth and Pioneer 11 measured in seconds.
